%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20THC%20beverage%20took%20off%20as%20people%20drank%20less%20alcohol.%20Now%20it%20could%20disappear.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Tidwell%20(left)%20and%20Anthony%20Puterman%20(right)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695ec8bc64858d02d217f21d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENowadays%20was%20founded%20in%202023%20by%20CEO%20Justin%20Tidwell%20and%20Anthony%20Puterman.%3Cp%3ENowadays%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENowadays%20THC%20beverage%20brand%20faces%20a%20potential%20ban%20under%20a%20bill%20set%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20in%20November%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20has%20found%20that%20demand%20for%20alcohol%20alternatives%20is%20growing%20among%20adults.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENowadays%20CEO%20Justin%20Tidwell%20said%20he%20has%20less%20than%20a%20year%20to%20convince%20regulators%20to%20amend%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20weed%20crumbs%20mixed%20into%20water%20is%20becoming%20a%20go-to%20drink%20of%20choice%20for%20adults%20who%20want%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20buzz%20than%20alcohol%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20a%20leading%20THC%20beverage%20brand%2C%20was%20founded%20in%20March%202023%20by%20Anthony%20Puterman%20and%20CEO%20Justin%20Tidwell.%20Less%20than%20three%20years%20later%2C%20its%20popularity%20has%20exploded%2C%20with%20sales%20jumping%20270%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025%20from%20the%20same%20period%20in%202024%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20from%20this%20is%20a%20cool%20pet%20project%20to%20something%20where%20we%20see%20a%20massive%20consumer%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Tidwell%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%20has%20built%20up%20quite%20the%20following%2C%20which%20Tidwell%20says%20is%20mostly%20made%20up%20of%20adult%20women%20of%20varying%20ages.%20From