%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIndonesia%2C%20home%20to%20the%20world's%20fourth-largest%20population%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-elon-musk-xai-explained-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebarred%20access%20to%20Grok%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20generated%20sexualized%20images%20of%20real%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndonesia's%20Ministry%20of%20Communications%20said%20it%20is%20temporarily%20suspending%20access%20to%20Grok%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20women%2C%20children%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20community%20from%20the%20risk%20of%20fake%20pornographic%20content%20generated%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20views%20the%20practice%20of%20non-consensual%20sexual%20deepfakes%20as%20a%20serious%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20the%20security%20of%20citizens%20in%20the%20digital%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Meutya%20Hafid%2C%20the%20minister%20of%20communications%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20xAI%20makes%20Grok%20and%20also%20owns%20X%2C%20which%20integrates%20the%20bot%20into%20its%20platform.%20Indonesia%20is%20home%20to%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20number%20of%20X%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorld%20governments%20have%20taken%20aim%20at%20Grok%20after%20some%20used%20it%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-remove-clothes-ai-images-women-minors-backlash-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigitally%20undress%20real%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20photos%2C%20and%20then%20post%20them%20to%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20authorities%20told%20Politico%20this%20month%20that%20they%20will%20investigate%20sexually%20explicit%20deepfakes%20generated%20by%20Grok.%20And%20the%20Indian%20government%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20X's%20chief%20compliance%20representative%20in%20the%20country%20that%20Grok%20is%20being%