ounts%2C%20and%20working%20with%20local%20governments%20and%20law%20enforcement%20as%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20backlash%2C%20Grok's%20AI%20image%20generator%20is%20now%20limited%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-limits-grok-ai-image-tool-sexualized-deepfake-backlash-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epaying%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findonesia-bans-grok-generating-sexual-deepfakes-women-children-ai-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768075607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69629274832e0ef1ead78d14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findonesia-bans-grok-generating-sexual-deepfakes-women-children-ai-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22World%20governments%20have%20taken%20aim%20at%20Elon%20Musk's%20Grok%20chatbot%2C%20which%20has%20generated%20sexualized%20AI%20images%20of%20real%20women%20and%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findonesia-bans-grok-generating-sexual-deepfakes-women-children-ai-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tom%20Cherones%2C%20%E2%80%98Seinfeld%E2%80%99%20Producer%20and%20Director%2C%20Dies%20at%2086%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768075160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2026%2F01%2FTC.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236628041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tom%20Cherones%2C%20the%20director%20and%20producer%20best%20known%20for%20working%20on%2081%20of%20the%20first%2086%20episodes%20of%20%E2%80%9CSeinfeld%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20show%E2%80%99s%20fi