0local%20grandmother%20was%20so%20upset%20at%20being%20second%20fiddle%20that%20she%20sulked%20through%20the%20party%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20stress%20for%20the%20mother.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20grandmother's%20selfish%20behavior%20only%20damaged%20her%20own%20relationship%20with%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa4deba5-f2cf-43e3-b498-08d47e8f900d%5C%22%3EGive%20without%20expectations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20OK%20to%20have%20expectations%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20but%20they%20can%20create%20conflict%20if%20they're%20not%20clearly%20articulated.%20I%20see%20this%20all%20the%20time%20between%20grandparents%20and%20their%20own%20children.%20A%20grandparent%20might%20feel%20that%20paying%20for%20a%20child's%20schooling%20gives%20them%20the%20entitlement%20to%20critique%20educational%20decisions%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222062%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dale%20Atkins%20with%20her%20family%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6958024064858d02d217aabe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDale%20Atkins%20says%20grandparents%20should%20show%20up%20for%20things%20their%20grandkids%20are%20interested%20in.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dale%20Atkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20choose%20to%20give%2C%20it's%20best%20not%20to%20expect%20anything%20in%20return.%20If%20you%20%3Cem%3Edo%3C%2Fem%3E%20expect%20something%20%E2%80%94%20like%20weekly%20family%20dinners%20in%20exchange%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-saved-childcare-costs-by-swapping-babysitting-with-a-mom-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoccasional%20babysitting%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20convey%20that%20to%20your%20family%2C%20and%20have%20an%20honest%20conversation.%20It's%20OK%20to%20ask%20for%20things%2C%20but%20not%20to%20demand%20or%20threaten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0b2d41a-2017-4e70-9963-87a888b1eff7%5C%22%3ER