0the%20passion%20of%20our%20women%20artisans.%20We%20at%20Gul%20Jaipur%20are%20firm%20believers%20in%20the%20virtues%20of%20conscious%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20closely%20with%20our%20women%20artisans%20to%20guarantee%20that%20they%20receive%20their%20much-deserved%20recognition%20and%20working%20conditions%20while%20creating%20our%20products%20using%20their%20learned%20skill%20sets%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496049%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanya%20Setia%E2%80%99s%20Gul%20is%20another%20powerhouse%20of%20sustainability%20where%20beautiful%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20take%20shape.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDHOZUl0NIcI%2F%3Fimg_index%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%